<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Bluetooth on memoria digital</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/tags/bluetooth/</link><description>Recent content in Bluetooth on memoria digital</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>es-es</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://volteret4.github.io/notas/tags/bluetooth/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Detectar Dispositivos Bluetooth</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/detectar-dispositivos-bluetooth/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/detectar-dispositivos-bluetooth/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/73615751/how-to-detect-and-enable-a-bluetooth-adapter" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Origen&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>El kernel de Linux registrará todos los dispositivos conectados a él durante el inicio y puede encontrarlos con el siguiente commando.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">dmesg &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> grep -i blue
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Puedes usar &lt;code>bluetoothctl&lt;/code> para arrancar la app y luego usar:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">power on
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">agent on
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">scan on
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">connect MAC_ADDRESS
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">trust MAC_ADDRESS
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>